headline: 1 Wall Street Analyst Thinks Altria Stock Is Going to $65. Is It a Buy?
summary: Altria (NYSE: MO) is one of the stock market's more divisive titles.  It's safe to say there were more folks taking notice recently when one Wall Street analyst who tracks Altria upgraded her rating of it.  Before the trading day opened on Dec. 6, news broke that Bank of America's Lisa Lewandowski had changed her view on Altria.
